{"tid":1831141,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"北角聲哥厨房垃圾!!!!!!!!!!! 老闆鬧返客!!!!!!!!!!!","createTime":"2020-01-20T07:32:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T07:26:00.000Z","uid":296807,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"69586478608eddf8d2bd311ec345d27e24f46dd1","tid":1831141,"uid":296807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T07:32:07.000Z","msg":"藍店聲哥厨房 Shing&rsquo;s Kitchen位於北角丹拿道8號雋悅匯三樓，表示強烈不滿及投訴，原因如下：<br />\n<br />\n1) 這家餐廳是持有會員牌照, 我發現原來不是會員都可用膳, 這是明顯違反食環條例無牌經營食肆。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2)我們分別點了一客蒸瓜子班魚及煲仔飯，這兩道菜於上菜後，發現蒸魚未經煮熟完全不宜食用，煲仔飯的白飯仍是硬的就上菜給客人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3) 用膳回家後, 我們一行6人圴感到肚子不適, 其中2人更柯了4次以上，嚴重投訴這家餐廳食物不潔、不衛生、並不適宜供人食用。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4) 服務員態度惡劣，最後埋單時在收銀等了數分鐘服務員都沒有理會我, 更鬧返我收聲，全程黑口黑面，態度冷淡，工作緩慢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n5) 事後向老闆聲哥反映食物不佳及員工服務態度惡劣差, 反倒被聲哥一大指罵更cut線。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好再幫襯藍店啦 食左都背脊骨落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3196d0375af43da5f39263ea01feff08e87e579a","tid":1831141,"uid":248534,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T07:34:09.000Z","msg":"冇人叫你食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76e62778a84a0098913acd7f08d6f653982c81e0","tid":1831141,"uid":278990,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T07:35:14.000Z","msg":"call 左食環未"},{"pid":"9f1f0ec8532c583